name: INVINCIBLE
overview: Mark Grayson is a normal teenager except for the fact that his father is the most powerful superhero on the planet. Shortly after his seventeenth birthday, Mark begins to develop powers of his own and enters into his father’s tutelage.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Nolan Grayson (Omni-Man) is unquestionably the strongest being on our planet; he is also our most spirited protector, having saved the planet from untold calamity. His son Mark, wants nothing more than to follow in his footsteps. But there's something sinister afoot and Omni-man may not be what he appears. Which may prove even too much for the Guardians of the Globe.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In Season 2, still reeling from Nolan's betrayal, Mark struggles to rebuild his life as he faces a host of new threats, all while battling his greatest fear - that he might become his father without even knowing it.

episodes.name: IT'S ABOUT TIME
episodes.overview: When Mark Grayson finally inherits powers from his superhero father, it’s a dream come true. But there’s more to being a hero than just choosing a name and costume.

episodes.name: HERE GOES NOTHING
episodes.overview: With his father out of action, Mark struggles to defend the city against an interdimensional invasion, joining forces with a team of teenage superheroes.

episodes.name: WHO YOU CALLING UGLY?
episodes.overview: Mark has to cut a study date short to help save Mount Rushmore from a crazed scientist. Robot deals with Action - Comic as he assembles a new team of world-saving superheroes.

episodes.name: NEIL ARMSTRONG, EAT YOUR HEART OUT
episodes.overview: It's two firsts for Mark: a first date and a first trip to another planet. At the same time, Nolan and Debbie revisit their own first vacation together.

episodes.name: THAT ACTUALLY HURT
episodes.overview: Feeling confident in his new abilities, Mark risks a team-up with a local villain to take down a crime lord, while simultaneously juggling school and a new relationship.

guest_stars.character: Principal Winslow / Tether Tyrant / GDA Scientist (voice)
guest_stars.name: Reginald VelJohnson

episodes.name: YOU LOOK KINDA DEAD
episodes.overview: Mark joins William and Amber on a campus visit to Upstate University, hoping to discover a new future for himself. Debbie makes her own disturbing discovery.

episodes.name: WE NEED TO TALK
episodes.overview: Feeling lost and confused, Mark looks for advice from Eve. At the same time, everyone's looking for him.

guest_stars.character: Shrinking Rae / Monster Girl / GDA Tech (voice)
guest_stars.name: Grey DeLisle

episodes.name: WHERE I REALLY COME FROM
episodes.overview: Mark must prove he's become the hero he's always wanted to be by stopping an unstoppable force.

guest_stars.character: Shrinking Rae / Monster Girl / GDA Tech (voice)
guest_stars.name: Grey DeLisle

episodes.name: IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE
